      <div class=" clearFloats bigBox"><div class="h2Container gradientHeaderContainer"><h2 class="brownBackground"><a href="/work/quotes/3177604-le-livre-de-ma-m-re">Quotes from Book of My Mother</a></h2></div><div class="bigBoxBody"><div class="bigBoxContent containerWithHeaderContent">
          <div class="stacked" tyle="padding-bottom:15px">
            <span class="readable">&ldquo;Ma souffrance est ma vengeance contre moi-même.&rdquo;</span>
            <nobr>
